  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a large pot over medium heat until shimmering.",
    "Add diced onion and sauté until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in minced garlic, smoked paprika, cumin, and coriander, cooking for 1 minute until fragrant.",
    "Add diced cox apple and vegetable broth, bring to a gentle boil.",
    "Reduce heat and simmer for 20 minutes until apples soften.",
    "Use an immersion blender to puree the soup until silky smooth, then stir in coconut milk.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste, and let the soup heat through for 2 minutes.",
    "Ladle into bowls and serve hot, optionally garnishing with a drizzle of olive oil or fresh herbs."
